```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace("U", "Uq")

# Example usage
print(insert_after_character("quack"))  # returns "quqack"
print(insert_after_character("Quack"))  # returns "Qquack"
print(insert_after_character("quick"))  # returns "quick"
print(insert_after_character("QUICK"))  # returns "QUQICK"
```
